OL,3,CThe fish and chip shop which has just
OL,4,Cbeen crowned the best in the country
OL,6,FEach contender was reviewed by a panel
OL,7,Fof judges on its environmental
OL,8,Fstandards, sustainability best
OL,9,Fpractice methods, customer service and
OL,10,Fknowledge of the fish and chip
OL,11,Findustry.
OL,13,FKnights has been running for more than
OL,14,Fa century, and is no stranger to
OL,15,Fawards.
OL,17,FThe earliest records suggest the shop
OL,18,Fbegan in 1895, when the census
OL,19,Frecorded an Elizbeth Hockey selling
OL,20,Ffried fish from her home address on
OL,21,FNorthload Street.
