OL,6,FThe shop continues to be run as a
OL,7,Ffamily business today and has gone on
OL,8,Fto pick up numerous titles in more
OL,9,Frecent years, including being one of
OL,10,Fthe finalists for fish and chip
OL,11,Frestaurant of the year in 2020 and
OL,12,F2023.
OL,14,FThis year, the restaurant was named as
OL,15,Fthe best of them all, beating Eric's
OL,16,FFish and Chips, in Hunstanton;
OL,17,FCirencester's Malt and Anchor; Noah's,
OL,18,Fin Bristol, and Pier Point Restaurant
OL,19,Fin Torquay.
