OL,6,FSpeaking about the event, awards
OL,7,Forganiser and President of the
OL,8,FNational Federation of Fish Friers
OL,9,FAndrew Crook said: "The National Fish
OL,10,Fand Chip Awards 2024 has been a
OL,11,Fremarkable experience to be part of.
OL,13,F"Our winners and finalists have put
OL,14,Ftheir all into making their fish and
OL,15,Fchip businesses stand-out for all the
OL,16,Fright reasons.
