OL,3,CThe fish and chip shop which has just
OL,4,Cbeen crowned the best in the country
OL,6,F"It's no secret that the sector has
OL,7,Fbeen hit hard by economic hardship,
OL,8,Fyet we have seen first hand how
OL,9,Fchippies up and down the country, and
OL,10,Foverseas, are thinking fast on their
OL,11,Ffeet to defy the odds without
OL,12,Fcompromising on ethical standpoints,
OL,13,Fquality and most importantly, great
OL,14,Ftasting fish and chips.
OL,16,F"We are bursting with pride for our
OL,17,Fwinners and other contenders. It's a
OL,18,Fprivilege to be able to support and
OL,19,Fencourage them further and they should
OL,20,Fall be proud of what they've achieved.
